Package: SMAD
Type: Package
Title: Statistical Modelling of AP-MS Data (SMAD)
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Qingzhou", "Zhang", , "zqzneptune@hotmail.com", c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Qingzhou Zhang <zqzneptune@hotmail.com>
Description: This is an R package that implements statistical modelling 
    approaches that assign confidence scores to protein-protein interaction data 
    generated using affinity purification mass spectrometry (AP-MS) data.
